A '''Yunkai'i slave''' is a minor unnamed character first appearing in [[Season 3]]. She's played by [[Mustapha Mekanassi]] and only appeared in "[[Mhysa]]".
sections.Biography:
===[[Season 3]]===
She is one of the [[Slavery|slaves]] that are freed by [[Daenerys Targaryen]] following the Sack of [[Yunkai]]. When Daenerys greets the slaves of Yunkai and tells them that it is their own choice to reach for their freedom, she is one of the slaves shouting "mhysa" at Daenerys. When Daenerys steps into the crowd, she is one of the slaves who embraces her.<ref>[[Mhysa]]</ref>
